    <title>PostgreSQL 索引优化实战</title>
    <url>/2026/04/05/postgresql-index-optimization/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="PostgreSQL-索引优化实战"><a href="#PostgreSQL-索引优化实战" class="headerlink" title="PostgreSQL 索引优化实战"></a>PostgreSQL 索引优化实战</h1><p>数据库查询性能往往是系统瓶颈所在，合理使用索引能大幅提升查询速度。</p>
<h2 id="B-Tree-索引"><a href="#B-Tree-索引" class="headerlink" title="B-Tree 索引"></a>B-Tree 索引</h2><p>B-Tree 是 PostgreSQL 默认索引类型，适用于等值查询和范围查询：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 创建复合索引</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">CREATE</span> INDEX idx_posts_site_status <span class="keyword">ON</span> posts(site_id, status);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 分析查询计划</span></span><br><span class="line">EXPLAIN ANALYZE</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="operator">*</span> <span class="keyword">FROM</span> posts</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">WHERE</span> site_id <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;xxx&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">AND</span> status <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;published&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">ORDER</span> <span class="keyword">BY</span> created_at <span class="keyword">DESC</span></span><br><span class="line">LIMIT <span class="number">10</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="部分索引"><a href="#部分索引" class="headerlink" title="部分索引"></a>部分索引</h2><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 只索引已发布的文章</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">CREATE</span> INDEX idx_posts_published <span class="keyword">ON</span> posts(site_id, created_at <span class="keyword">DESC</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">WHERE</span> status <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;published&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">AND</span> deleted_at <span class="keyword">IS</span> <span class="keyword">NULL</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="监控慢查询"><a href="#监控慢查询" class="headerlink" title="监控慢查询"></a>监控慢查询</h2><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> query, mean_exec_time, calls</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">FROM</span> pg_stat_statements</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">ORDER</span> <span class="keyword">BY</span> mean_exec_time <span class="keyword">DESC</span></span><br><span class="line">LIMIT <span class="number">10</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>合理的索引设计可以让查询从秒级降到毫秒级。</p>
]]></content>
