    <title>NATS JetStream：消息队列的现代选择</title>
    <url>/2026/04/05/nats-jetstream-introduction/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="NATS-JetStream：消息队列的现代选择"><a href="#NATS-JetStream：消息队列的现代选择" class="headerlink" title="NATS JetStream：消息队列的现代选择"></a>NATS JetStream：消息队列的现代选择</h1><p>NATS JetStream 是 NATS 的持久化消息系统，提供 at-least-once 和 exactly-once 语义。</p>
<h2 id="基本概念"><a href="#基本概念" class="headerlink" title="基本概念"></a>基本概念</h2><ul>
<li><strong>Stream</strong>：消息存储单元，可配置保留策略</li>
<li><strong>Consumer</strong>：订阅 stream 并消费消息的实体</li>
<li><strong>Subject</strong>：消息路由的主题</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="Go-客户端示例"><a href="#Go-客户端示例" class="headerlink" title="Go 客户端示例"></a>Go 客户端示例</h2><figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> <span class="string">&quot;github.com/nats-io/nats.go/jetstream&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">nc, _ := nats.Connect(nats.DefaultURL)</span><br><span class="line">js, _ := jetstream.New(nc)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 创建 stream</span></span><br><span class="line">js.CreateStream(ctx, jetstream.StreamConfig&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    Name:     <span class="string">&quot;EVENTS&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    Subjects: []<span class="type">string</span>&#123;<span class="string">&quot;events.&gt;&quot;</span>&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 发布消息</span></span><br><span class="line">js.Publish(ctx, <span class="string">&quot;events.user.created&quot;</span>, []<span class="type">byte</span>(<span class="string">`&#123;&quot;user_id&quot;:&quot;123&quot;&#125;`</span>))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 消费消息</span></span><br><span class="line">cons, _ := js.CreateConsumer(ctx, <span class="string">&quot;EVENTS&quot;</span>, jetstream.ConsumerConfig&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    Durable: <span class="string">&quot;processor&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    AckPolicy: jetstream.AckExplicitPolicy,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">msgs, _ := cons.Messages()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> msg := <span class="keyword">range</span> msgs &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 处理消息</span></span><br><span class="line">    msg.Ack()</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="与-Kafka-对比"><a href="#与-Kafka-对比" class="headerlink" title="与 Kafka 对比"></a>与 Kafka 对比</h2><p>NATS JetStream 部署简单、延迟更低，适合中小规模的事件驱动架构。</p>
]]></content>
